Class LocalDriverConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class LocalDriverConfiguration
extends ConfigurationModuleBuilder
    ConfigurationModule for the Driver executed in the local resourcemanager. This is meant to eventually replace LocalDriverRuntimeConfiguration.
